Package: pavem
Title: Simple Panel VAR and Panel VECM Workflows
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("William", "Cantah", email = "williamcantah@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Beginner-friendly wrappers for cross-sectional dependence tests,
    panel unit-root tests, panel cointegration tests, Panel VAR estimation,
    Panel VECM estimation, post-estimation diagnostics, impulse-response
    tables and plots with confidence intervals, and forecast error variance
    decomposition tables and plots using existing CRAN econometrics packages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    plm,
    pco,
    panelvar,
    pvars,
    vars,
    stats,
    graphics,
    grDevices
Suggests:
    readxl,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
URL: https://github.com/williamcantah/pavem
BugReports: https://github.com/williamcantah/pavem/issues
